  <summary>Testing solution for APIs</summary>
  <description>
    <p>SoapUI is the world's leading Functional Testing tool for SOAP and REST testing. With its easy-to-use graphical interface, and enterprise-class features, SoapUI allows you to easily and rapidly create and execute automated functional, regression, and load tests.</p>
    <p>Folders used:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Open and save files: the user Documents folder (use Flatseal to allow acces to other folders)</li>
      <li>User directory for settings, actions, listeners, extensions and plugins: ~/.var/app/org.soapui.SoapUI/.soapuios/</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
